// Man page for arrow2
manArrow2=">>(1)                        X Shell Manual                        >>(1)

<b>NAME</b>
    command >> FILE - Append output to file
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Append command output to existing file. File must exist. All
    output goes to file, not terminal. Adds to end of file.
<b>EXAMPLE:</b>
    <b>echo New entry >> log.txt</b>
    Add line to log file

    <b>ps >> processes.txt</b>
    Append process list to file"